#

Honey Mustard Glazed Salmon with Asparagus

$25.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carbohydrate

Tags:

SeafoodHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A delightful blend of sweet and tangy honey mustard glaze complements perfectly baked salmon, served alongside tender asparagus for a nutritious and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 4 pieces
  • Honey: 3 tablespoons
  • Dijon mustard: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Asparagus: 1 pound
  • Garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
